t herald. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Formed by the union of: Wolf Point herald, and: Roosevelt County news. Vol. XXVII, No. 51 (January 18, 1940); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 16, 2024). Vol. 42, No. 49 (December 15, 1955) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 16, 2024)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:15.756Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271111/", "image_url": [], "index": 10, "language": ["english"], "location": ["wolf point", "united states", "roosevelt", "montana"], "number": ["2024271110", "2024271111", "online resource", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2997-8572", "1434062668"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the herald-news (wolf point, roosevelt county, montana) 1940-current [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 24.69737, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["montana", "united states", "newspapers", "wolf point (mont.)", "roosevelt", "wolf point"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:57.142Z", "title": "The herald-news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271111/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271284/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1913", "dates": ["[1913 TO 1940]"], "description": ["Weekly Began in 1913; ceased v. 27, no. 50 (Jan. 10, 1940). Merged with: Roosevelt County news, to form: Herald-news (Wolf Point, Mont.). Description based on: Volume VII. No. 45. (Janaury 1, 1920); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 21, 2020). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XX, Number Forty-Seven (December 30, 1932) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 21, 2020). Roosevelt County news Herald-news (Wolf Point, Mont.)"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:58.293Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271284/", "image_url": [], "index": 11, "language": ["english"], "location": ["wolf point", "united states", "roosevelt", "montana"], "number": ["2766-2861", "2020271284", "online resource", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "1227507470"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the wolf point herald (wolf point, montana) 1913-1940 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 24.69737, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["montana", "united states", "newspapers", "wolf point (mont.)", "roosevelt", "wolf point"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:01:07.415Z", "title": "The Wolf Point herald", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020271284/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2013271999/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1902", "dates": ["[1902 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Weekly Began April 24, 1902. \"Republican.\" Cf. Montana newspaper directories. \"Official paper of Valley County,\" June 15-Dec. 1, 1904; \"official paper of Sheridan County,\" June 12, 1914-June 4, 1915; official paper of Roosevelt County, Jan. 24, 1936-Feb. 16, 1940. Suspended: Aug. 6-Oct. 1, 1942. Description based on: Vol. VII, no. 38 (Jan. 1, 1909); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 23, 2014). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XI, no. 36 (Dec. 27, 1912) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 23, 2014)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:24.080Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013271999/", "image_url": [], "index": 12, "language": ["english"], "location": ["culbertson